                Every tagged problem is plotted on a 2√ó2 matrix so you know what to automate first.
              </p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-[#d0d8e6]">Axes Covered:</p>
              <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-6 text-sm text-[#cbd4e6] space-y-1">
                <li>X-AXIS: Business Impact (Low ‚Üí High)</li>
                <li>Y-AXIS: Implementation Effort (Easy ‚Üí Hard)</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
                {matrixQuadrants.map((quadrant) => (
                  <div class="rounded-xl border border-[#ffffff15] bg-white/5 p-4">
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">{quadrant.name}</p>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#d0d8e6] leading-relaxed">{quadrant.description}</p>
                  </div>
                ))}
              </div>
              <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[#d0d8e6]">
                VALUE: No more analysis paralysis‚Äîyou know exactly which AI initiatives deliver maximum ROI.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[#151a33]/70 p-5">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/95">3. üó∫Ô∏è THE IMPLEMENTATION ROADMAP (Your 12-Month Plan)</p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-white/80">
                We stack opportunities into a phased roadmap so you execute in the smartest order possible.
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-sm text-[#cbd4e6]">
                {roadmapPhases.map((phase) => (
                  <li>{phase}</li>
                ))}
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[#d0d8e6]">
                VALUE: A clear, actionable plan showing exactly what to implement when‚Äîno overwhelm, no guesswork.
