            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/15 bg-white/5 p-5">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[#7ee8ff]">COLLABORATIVE VALIDATION SESSION</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-white">
            Before finalizing recommendations, we review the Opportunity Matrix with your leadership team. It‚Äôs a working session‚Äîpriorities are adjusted based on reality so you own the roadmap, not just observe it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-[30px] border border-white/10 bg-[#0f1220]/85 p-8 shadow-[0_35px_90px_rgba(4,6,14,0.65)]">
      <header class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-white">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[#7ee8ff] [font-family:'Segoe_UI_Symbol-Regular',Helvetica]">
          STEP 3
        </p>
        <h3 class="[font-family:'Segoe_UI_Symbol-Regular',Helvetica] text-2xl md:text-3xl">THE ROI PRESENTATION ‚Äî PROVING THE BUSINESS CASE</h3>
        <p class="text-base text-[#cbd4e6] [font-family:'Segoe_UI_Symbol-Regular',Helvetica]">End of Week 2 ‚Ä¢ Executive Presentation</p>
      </header>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-[#d0d8e6] [font-family:'Segoe_UI_Symbol-Regular',Helvetica]">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[#f78bc0]">WHAT HAPPENS</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-white/90">
            We present a comprehensive executive report that translates everything into dollars and cents. You'll know exactly what each opportunity costs to implement and what financial return to expect‚Äîno leaps of faith.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-[24px] border border-white/15 bg-white/5 p-6">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[#7ee8ff]">YOUR EXECUTIVE PRESENTATION INCLUDES</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-3 pl-6 text-sm text-[#d0d8e6]">
            {executivePresentationItems.map((item) => (
